description: Lanna is the main character of my published book "Linha Tênue" (Thin Line) - https://linktr.ee/carolinaleao • The video cover was the first vision I ever had of her, I did it in watercolor. This art is really special and important to me. Moon's photograph is also really meaningful, first clear natural satellite picture I ever took. The video tells the tale of how the first werewolf arised, an important part of my book. This story goes 10 years back in my life.
